<h1>Breakfast</h1>
<p>We had some seaside porridge with abalone. Not the kind of breakfast I am used to, but if you like seafood, this is actually pretty good. This is traditional old-school Korean food, stuff your mom or grandma eats for breakfast. Try it if you want an (old-school) Korean breakfast.</p>
